{"tid":2492191,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王貽興抽水轟老狗「阻住地球轉」，翻曾志偉酒後狂言舊帳","createTime":"2021-04-17T02:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T02:45:33.000Z","uid":31314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ab8613052d08f76ead088d1968c896a222cd85","tid":2492191,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:27:46.000Z","msg":"曾志偉回巢無綫後是非特別多，日前插完ViuTV得4點收視冇得同無綫比較，即被193@ERROR寸爆反擊，估唔到曾經為無綫主持節目的王貽興亦加入戰團，他在個人社交網轉載一篇本刊於14年的報導，逢飲必醉的曾志偉出席活動酒後口出狂言，直指「TVB係弱台！」王才子借題發揮撰寫長文直指獎門人脫節、阻住地球轉，狂翻曾志偉舊帳<br />\n<br />\n曾志偉回巢無綫出任副總經理兼行政委員會特別顧問，意氣風發狂踩ViuTV，搞完個《開心大綜藝》首播又自high，覺得自己好威威，不過就被ViuTV的193反寸個台係畀老人家睇，曾志偉未有公開回應，而曾為無綫做主持的王貽興就湊熱鬧，轉載了一篇關於曾志偉飲醉酒話TVB是弱台的舊報道，並撰寫了一篇長文，<strong><span class=\"red\">內容大意是插獎門人過晒氣唔識與時並進，王貽興更大膽指曾志偉有預言能力，暗寸TVB是弱智台，用詞極度不留情面。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/F0qLeOZK0fTIbAe8dz9kxw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTEwNDMuOTQyMzA3NjkyMzA3NjtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/IL2nd9WkyrcpejDPEK7Ehw--~B/aD01Mzk7dz0zNjQ7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/orientalsundayent.com/d49b710fa4fddbf0892dcef3529b69c3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FF0qLeOZK0fTIbAe8dz9kxw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTEwNDMuOTQyMzA3NjkyMzA3NjtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIL2nd9WkyrcpejDPEK7Ehw--~B%2FaD01Mzk7dz0zNjQ7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Forientalsundayent.com%2Fd49b710fa4fddbf0892dcef3529b69c3&h=b780f35c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n16年與無綫提前解約<br />\n王貽興當年為無綫主持電視節目《最緊要正字》上位，07年正式簽約無綫成為旗下藝員，主持多個節目《一網打盡》、《謎》、《最緊要進步》，<strong><span class=\"red\">16年他在訪問中自爆已和無綫提前解約，據知是因為他對無綫的山頭文化及制度不滿，當時他透露只對文化藝術或發放深度信息的節目有興趣，不希望做那些沒有意義又「老馮」的節目，更發覺到香港的電視圈生態非常有問題</span></strong>，可見王貽興對無綫早已諸多不滿。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_RthmcAWsHwbGLchO1sPkw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgwNi4yNTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/X2_dSO1tP9NuZk0n6lV1GA--~B/aD04NjA7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/orientalsundayent.com/4d9eb5e7b2b4fc3d62b8ded325e79c54\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_RthmcAWsHwbGLchO1sPkw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgwNi4yNTtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FX2_dSO1tP9NuZk0n6lV1GA--~B%2FaD04NjA7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F4d9eb5e7b2b4fc3d62b8ded325e79c54&h=431beec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n翻查紀錄，原來2014年曾志偉呢次口出狂言，似乎唔係咁簡單，背後玄機，早已同余詠珊嘅鬥爭有關⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SLdCLBxK4o28NFUBUD5z6g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3NS42MjU7Y2Y9d2VicA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/r5PHNV_kUFFMeyp2ey7HRQ--~B/aD02MTQ7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/orientalsundayent.com/2a672091d2c35c87f524c706aa1b4433\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSLdCLBxK4o28NFUBUD5z6g--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3NS42MjU7Y2Y9d2VicA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fr5PHNV_kUFFMeyp2ey7HRQ--~B%2FaD02MTQ7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F2a672091d2c35c87f524c706aa1b4433&h=3881b98c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf391210c9a11c034ef0609307cf19efd24fcffc","tid":2492191,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:45:33.000Z","msg":"群起杯葛<br />\n追打落水狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}